isles2022-2d3d-blend-reproducible-pipeline
Copyright 2026 yskfuji

This repository is provided as a research/reproducibility and portfolio package
for ISLES 2022 ischemic stroke lesion segmentation using a heterogeneous
ensemble of 2D nnU-Net, MPS-compatible 3D nnU-Net, and 2.5D ConvNeXt models,
combined via cross-architecture probability fusion with adaptive thresholding.

It is NOT a medical device and is NOT intended for clinical decision making.

No datasets, trained weights, runs, results, or logs are included in this
repository. Users must obtain the ISLES-2022 dataset separately and comply
with the applicable data use agreement.

